---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 132
  - Title: Yoga-Vasishtha
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Sacrifice and Suffering=Sacrifice
  - Sacrifice-Death=Death=The Destruction of I-Consciousness
---
He is said to have made the greatest sacrifice who has sacrificed his own
mind and endeavours at the shrine of self-abnegation.
